data.title: King Harald V
data.meta_description: King Harald V. Self: Til Vesterheimen. King Harald V was born on 21 February 1937 in Oslo, Norway. He is an actor, known for Til Vesterheimen (1939), Stortinget (1995) and Dagsrevyen (1958). He has been married to Dronning Sonja since 29 August 1968. They have two children.
data.text:
King Harald V was born on 21 February 1937 in Oslo, Norway. He is an actor, known for Til Vesterheimen (1939), Stortinget (1995) and Dagsrevyen (1958). He has been married to Dronning Sonja since 29 August 1968. They have two children.
